overview: December's annual instruments of destruction event features "The Head of the Table" Roman Reigns defending his Universal Championship against Kevin Owens, as well as WWE Champion Drew McIntyre taking on AJ Styles for the WWE Championship happening in a TLC match. Randy Orton also faces "The Fiend" Bray Wyatt in a Firefly Inferno Match.
title: WWE TLC: Tables, Ladders & Chairs 2020
